{"tid":2497123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場： 政府突改例 去年立會參選人如被指違國安法 不會獲發全數選舉開支","createTime":"2021-04-20T09:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T10:17:06.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a743f8303c028dcec658edeffe5bd98ef82e0a","tid":2497123,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"原定去年 9 月舉行的立法會換屆選舉最終押後一年，政府曾宣布已報名的參選人可獲發還全數選舉開支；但「民權觀察」成員沈偉男今日發文指，政府更新了立法會選舉開支指引，列明提出申索的候選人如因涉違反國安法而正接受調查或被刑事起訴，當局不得向有關候選人支付任何款項，直至調查或法律程序被最終裁定；若候選人最終被法庭裁定因牽涉非法的選舉活動而觸犯國安法，將一律失去收取政府付款的資格。<br />\n<br />\n沈偉男接受《立場新聞》訪問時批評當局事隔大半年方修改指引是「完全違反程序公義」，認為此舉是為了封殺民主派。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4091719517580304/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4091719517580304%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=a4b6b5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4091719517580304/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"87e72a83fd1bb143393f1393205b7997b3c98b4d","tid":2497123,"uid":82938,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"捉埋你坐監<br />\n其他野仲重要？"},{"pid":"2bb5f6e829f5ff025016b76e25da1a4bac4a03d1","tid":2497123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daac8f564411a1896d77ffcc5e128d1a507c865","tid":2497123,"uid":13000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T09:53:58.00